<Body>  <Title>福州：城门一棉花厂突发火灾 烧了五小时</Title>
	<ReportTime type="abs">2009-8-8</ReportTime>
<Content>

	
		<Paragraph> 
                <Sentence>
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">台海网</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t1">8月8日</Time><Denoter type="statement" did="d1">讯</Denoter></Event>
                （海峡都市报记者 吴臻 游庆辉  通讯员 黄绿荣 王福军  朱晓航 文/图）
                 <Event eid="e2">
                 <Time type="relTime" tid="t2">6日11时30分许</Time>，<Location lid="l2">福州城门胪厦工业区内</Location><Object sid="s2,s4">一棉花厂</Object>突发<Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">火灾</Denoter></Event>
                 ，
                 <Event eid="e3"><Object sid="s3">火势</Object>迅速<Denoter type="movement" did="d3">蔓延</Denoter></Event>
                 ，
                 <Event eid="e4"><Denoter type="operation" did="d4">殃及</Denoter>隔壁的<Object oid="o4">制鞋厂</Object></Event>
                 ，
                 <Event eid="e5"><Object sid="s5">上千平方米的仓库</Object>顿时<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d5">成为火海</Denoter></Event>
                 ，火烧红了城门半边天。
                 </Sentence>
                 <Sentence>
                 <Event eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">消防</Participant>在<Denoter type="action" did="d6">接到</Denoter><Object oid="o6">报警</Object>后</Event>
                 ，
                 <Event eid="e7">共<Denoter type="operation" did="d7">调</Denoter>来了<Participant oid="o7">6个中队</Participant>、<Object oid="o7">23部消防车</Object></Event>
                 ，
                 <Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8">一百多名消防官兵</Participant><Denoter type="movement" did="d8">赶赴</Denoter><Location  type="destination" lid="l8">火灾现场</Location></Event>
                 ，
                 <Event eid="e9">在<Time type="timeInterval" tid="t9">经过了5个小时的扑救后</Time>，<Object oid="o9">大火</Object>被<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">扑灭</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
                 
		<Paragraph>
                <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e10"><Time type="relTime" tid="t10">昨日凌晨</Time>，<Participant sid="s10">记者</Participant><Denoter type="movement" did="d10">赶到</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l10">现场</Location></Event>
                ，
                <Event eid="e11"><Location lid="l11">在数百米外</Location>就能<Denoter type="perception" did="d11">看到</Denoter><Object oid="o11">远处腾起的滚滚浓烟</Object></Event>
                ，
                <Event eid="e12"><Object sid="s12">红色的火光</Object><Denoter  type="operation" did="d12">照红</Denoter>了<Object oid="o12">城门大半边天</Object></Event>
                。
                </Sentence>
                <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e13"><Object sid="s13">着火的制鞋厂四楼仓库</Object>已<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d13">成火海</Denoter></Event>
                。</Sentence>
                <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">记者</Participant><Denoter type="action" did="d14">跟随</Denoter><Participant oid="o14">消防人员</Participant></Event>
                <Event eid="e15"><Denoter type="action" did="d15">登上</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l15">距离火场50米外的一厂房楼顶</Location></Event>时，
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e16">顿时<Denoter type="perception" did="d16">感到</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e17"><Object sid="s17">滚烫的热气</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d17">迎面扑来</Denoter></Event>
                。</Sentence>
                <Sentence>救火的消防队员都戴着空气呼吸器等防护装备。</Sentence></Paragraph>
                
		<Paragraph><Sentence>据了解，起火点是工业区内一棉花厂，与制鞋厂仅一墙之隔</Sentence>。</Paragraph>
		
		<Paragraph>
                <Sentence>
                <Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e18"><Participant sid="s18">目击者陈先生</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d18">说</Denoter></Event>，鞋厂仓库面积约1400平方米，里面堆放着大量成品拖鞋，另外棉花厂内还有大量棉花。</Sentence><Sentence>
                <Event eid="e19"><Denoter type="emergency" did="d19">火灾</Denoter>发生</Event>后，
                <Event eid="e20"><Object sid="s20">火势</Object><Denoter type="movement" did="d20">蔓延</Denoter>很快</Event>，
                <Event eid="e21">不久<Object sid="s21">大火</Object>就<Denoter type="action" did="d21">蹿</Denoter>上<Location type="destination" lid="l21">制鞋厂的四楼仓库</Location></Event>，一下子变得无法控制。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph>
                <Sentence>
                <Event  type="thoughtevent" eid="e22"><Participant sid="s22">消防队员</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d22">告诉</Denoter><Participant oid="o22">记者</Participant></Event>，由于火场周边地形复杂，水源匮乏，
                <Event eid="e23"><Participant sid="s23">现场指挥部</Participant>决定<Denoter type="operation" did="d23">调集</Denoter><Object oid="o23">大型水罐车</Object>进行远距离接力供水</Event>，保证往火场一线进行不间断供水。</Sentence>
                <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e24"><Location lid="l24">周边工厂</Location>的<Participant sid="s24">工人和群众</Participant>也纷纷<Denoter type="action" did="d24">拿</Denoter>出厂里的<Object oid="o24">水带</Object></Event>， 
                <Event eid="e25">还<Denoter  type="action" did="d25">找</Denoter>出了为数不多的<Object oid="o25">消火栓</Object></Event>，
                <Event eid="e26"><Denoter type="operation" did="d26">协助</Denoter><Participant oid="o26">消防官兵</Participant></Event>
                <Event eid="e27"><Denoter type="operation" did="d27">控制</Denoter><Object oid="o27">火势</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
                
		<Paragraph>
                <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e28"><Time  type="timeInterval" tid="t28">直到昨日凌晨4点40分左右</Time>，<Object oid="o28">大火</Object>被成功<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d28">扑灭</Denoter></Event>，
                <Event polarity="negative" eid="e29">所幸火灾没有造成<Participant sid="s29">人员</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d29">伤亡</Denoter></Event>
                。</Sentence>
                <Sentence>
                <Event eid="e30"><Time type="relTime" tid="t30">目前</Time>，<Object oid="o30">火灾原因</Object>还在<Denoter type="operation" did="d30">调查</Denoter>当中</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
                
  
